Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,no case is left unsolved\Nwith Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that day, we set off to Akebonocho\Nin order to arrest a serial thief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,@onan, let¢s catch the thief no\Nmatter wat it takes, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y.Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it feel A bit eerie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have other people take\Nover and use what can still be used
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,cherishing what limited resources we\Nhave. I'd say it's a splendid arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean recycling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you don't know who the stuff was\Nbeing used by previously, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need for worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there is nobody who rubs snot\Non everything like you do, Genta.
