Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you see any suspicious\NIooking people. be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah gee. what the heck am I doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up. Conan!
