Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it okay conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is\Ncerebral contusion from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,being hit in the back of his\Nhead with a blunt object.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is between\N2:00 pm to 3-004 yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had nothing on him that\Nwould help us identify him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. HOsSONO...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,willyyou please explain in detail the\Ncondition in which you found the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sofa, is what I bought yesterday at\Nsundown at a recycle shop at Beikacho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I had it delivered here\Nat about 10:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, after taking a good look,\Nthe sheet was a little out of place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I attempted to put it back in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found that lady inside the sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, and do you\Nhave any idea who the victim is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you yesterday betweenl\Nthe hours of 14:00 and 15.007?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A. Are you suspecting me?
