Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at the movies\Nyesterday afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was somebody else with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Inspector\NMegure suspects her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are two things\Nthat-are~thinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sanae Hosono\Nkilled the victim and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made it look like the corpse was inside\Nthe sofa that was delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other is, a sofa with the corpse\Ninside it is delivered just like she said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when:we over there she\Nreally looked.surprised and pale!
