Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the job of the police\Nto consider all possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But .
