Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she was killed. she was\Nprobably not wearing her shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! Which means\Nshe was killed in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she is the killer,\Nthe site of the crime is in this room
