Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. that se>fa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an item that we bought\Nfrom a customer yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday?
