Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it was loaded on\Nthe truck for delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A oN °\NS ere any possiianity ra someone\Nfrom outside can get near the truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible because the truck\NIS parked inside the warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the\Nwarehouse is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the old lady was in there\Nalready when it was purchased...
