Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you were told to take the\Nsofa, even if it were for free
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, yesterday\Nafternoon, on the way back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after I went to purchase items\Nin several places in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was around 16:00...
