Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:09:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But manager. I felt it so\Nwasteful to be thrown away
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iike that when it still\NIooked so usable, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I lied...
